***********************************************
Available commands:

>> online
Shows all available users on the server. This list
is refreshed every 10 seconds.

>> message <username>
Send a message to a user named "username". After this command
you will be prompted to fill in the message.

>> show <username>
Display last 20 messages exchanged with the user identified by his username.

>> logout
Logout from the server and exit the application.
***********************************************